<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/58524608-why-they-stay"><img alt="Why They Stay: Sex Scandals, Deals, and Hidden Agendas of Eight Political Wives" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1625880812l/58524608._SX98_.jpg" />
